OL,7,FThe children of a woman killed by a
OL,8,Fmurderer serving a whole-life sentence
OL,9,Fhave described how the possibility of
OL,10,Fhis release from prison on
OL,11,F"compassionate grounds" makes their
OL,12,F"blood boil" and would be a "national
OL,13,Fscandal".
OL,15,FVictor Farrant was jailed for life for
OL,16,Fthe murder of his former girlfriend
OL,17,FGlenda Hoskins, 44, and the attempted
OL,18,Fmurder of Ann Fidler, 45, at
OL,19,FWinchester Crown Court in 1998.
