OL,7,FSentencing him, Mr Justice Butterfield
OL,8,Fhad said: "This murder was so terrible
OL,9,Fand you are so dangerous that in your
OL,10,Fcase the sentence of life should mean
OL,11,Fjust that.
OL,13,F"You should never be released."
