OL,16,Flast month they had been contacted by
OL,17,Fofficials who said that Farrant was
OL,18,Fbeing considered for compassionate
OL,19,Fleave as he had been diagnosed with
OL,20,Fterminal cancer and could have months
OL,21,Fto live.
